install gpsd and geoclue

gpsd must running on 127.0.0.1

this is normal when you plugin a usb device or connect the gpsd  to a gpsd server


git clone https://github.com/spookyfirehorse/gpsd-chrome-polyfill-master.git

cd gpsd-chrome-polyfill-master

python3 gps-ws.py &

go in chrome to developer tools  (  search in the directory the folder crx inside pollyfill ) install it

klick on the symbol in the taskbar 
